	    </tbody>
	  </tgroup>
	</table>

	<table frame="none">
	  <title>Verf&uuml;gbare Qt4-Plugin-Komponenten</title>

	  <tgroup cols="2">
	    <thead>
	      <row>
		<entry>Name</entry>
		<entry>Beschreibung</entry>
	      </row>
	    </thead>

	    <tbody>
	      <row>
		<entry><literal>iconengines</literal></entry>
		<entry>SVG-Icon-Engine Plugin (wenn die Applikation
		  SVG-Icons mitliefert)</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry><literal>imageformats</literal></entry>
		<entry>Bildformatplugins f&uuml;r GIF, JPEG, MNG und
